y=\"9\"></rect><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>LinkedIn</a></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-[#0F1A14]/80\"><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Ben Callis is a visionary technical founder and CEO whose grit and determination are second to none. </p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Before founding Ivy House, Callis made a name for himself by playing a critical role in shaping several successful startups&#x27; product strategies and designs in the mortgage, business intelligence, and education sectors. </p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">His expertise in these areas is evident in the accolades and achievements of the companies he has worked with.</p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">Callis is highly skilled with an education from the prestigious MIT and Sloan School of Management. He has also completed several cohorts at the Stanford D school, further honing his skills in design and innovation.</p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">But Callis&#x27;s contributions to the industry go far beyond his professional accomplishments.</p><p class=\"mb-4 leading-relaxed\">He is passionate about teaching and mentoring, teaching coding and UX design to over 5,000 students. He is also actively engaged in cultivating new talent by sharing his knowledge and network.&quot;</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"border-t border-[color:var(--color-border-gold)] pt-12\"><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl text-[color:var(--color-indigo)] mb-8\">Writing &amp; research</h2><div class=\"space-y-10\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open text-[color:var(--color-gold)]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><pat